About
====================
This is a video addon for sc2casts.com for xbmc.

Features
====================
* Browsing of Lastest/Most viewed
* Playback of vods hosted on youtube

Installing
====================
* If you do not have the youtube addon installed already add it through the addonmanager
* Download https://github.com/downloads/sucuriju/plugin.video.sc2casts.com/plugin.video.sc2casts.com-0.0.4.zip
* Start xbmc and navigate to system -> add-ons -> install from zip file, browse to the file.
* Use the add-on from the add-ons item in the video-browser.

Known issues
====================
Only plays Youtube casts, not listing others.
